reviewText: A dark funny foreign movie about Santa Claus but probably not for young children
this movie is great, i recommend anybody with an off beat sense of humor buy this.
One of the best Christmas movies ever! Watch it with "Bad Santa," Bad Santa 2," and "A Christmas Story."
Onni Tomilla is a great young actor.  Interesting and beautiful Finnish scenery in his movies.  Also starred in Big Game with Samuel Jackson.
